{"title":"莱茵河流过的地方","authors":["艾青"],"dates":[{"year":1979,"month":8,"day":15}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"莱茵河流过的地方"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"艾青"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"墙"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一堵墙，象一把刀"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把一个城市切成两片"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一半在东方"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一半在西方"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"墙有多高？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有多厚？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有多长？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"再高、再厚、再长"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"也不可能比中国的长城"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"更高、更厚、更长"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"它也只是历史的陈迹"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"民族的创伤"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"谁也不喜欢这样的墙"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"三米高算得了什么"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"五十厘米厚算得了什么"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"四十五公里长算得了什么"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"再高一千倍"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"再厚一千倍"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"再长一千倍"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"又怎能阻挡"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"天上的云彩、风、雨和阳光？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"又怎能阻挡"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"飞鸟的翅膀和夜莺的歌唱？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"又怎能阻挡"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"流动的水和空气？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"又怎能阻挡"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"千百万人的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"比风更自由的思想？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"比土地更深厚的意志？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"比时间更漫长的愿望？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一九七九年五月"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"二十二日波恩"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"访马克思故居"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"特里尔——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"绿色的夹谷里的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"古老的小城"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"特里尔"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有许多古罗马的遗迹"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"特里尔"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"经受过异族的入侵"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"青青的摩泽河"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"流过特里尔"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"流到莱茵河"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"摩泽河两岸"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"都是葡萄园"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"摩泽酒是醉人的名酒"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"特里尔是好客的小城"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"亚洲人、非洲人"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"美洲人、澳大利亚人"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"都来访问特里尔"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不是为了喝摩泽酒"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不是为了访问古迹名胜"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"而是因为这个小城里"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"曾经诞生了一个"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们这个世纪最伟大的人"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"五月二十三日特里尔"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"导游人"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"特里尔是一个可爱的古城"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"特里尔有一个可爱的导游人"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我不知道她的姓名"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"她有一双妩媚的眼睛"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从她薄薄的嘴唇里"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"流出最悦耳的声音"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"她象一个牧羊姑娘"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"热心地带领着羊群"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"也象一个历史教员"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"学识渊博而有耐心"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从选侯的宫殿"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"说到新教的教堂"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从西罗马的都城"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"说到大帝康士坦丁"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"以及拿破仑的入侵"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"到马克思的诞生"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从普鲁士人的占领"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"到特里尔的今天"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不断地以机智和幽默"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"博得了旅游者的笑声"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在短短的两个小时里"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"说完了两千年的事情"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"穿过黑城来到喷水池边"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"她微笑着和大家告别"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从此谁也没有再见她"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"但心里却响着泉水的声音"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"五月二十三日特里尔"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"死亡的纪念碑"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这是一个葡萄架？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这是一些藤蔓？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这是一堆废铁？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这是一些破烂？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"都不是，都不是"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"请你仔细看一看"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这是一些挂在铁丝网上的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"尸体"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一个个都瘦骨嶙峋"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"伸出了无援的手"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"发出了绝望的叫喊"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"抗议的控诉"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"象拉响了的汽笛"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"尖厉地震响在蓝天下"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"震响在每个人的耳边"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这些声音"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"越过了时间的坚壁"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一直通向未来的世纪"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"永远——永远……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"五月二十八日"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"慕尼黑达豪集中营"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"慕尼黑"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"慕尼黑"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"象巴伐利亚啤酒店的主妇"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"身体健康而有风韵"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"谁见到她都要钟情"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"但是"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"慕尼黑的名声不好"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大家都在咒骂她"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把她看作灾祸的象征"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"因为她"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"曾经和一个纵火犯鬼混"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那是个十足的流氓"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"比魔鬼还要恶三分"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"还有一个带伞的英国人"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"还有一个窄额头的法国人"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"三个人一边喝啤酒"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一边把邻居出卖了"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"接着是整个欧罗巴"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"升起了熊熊大火"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"连慕尼黑她自己"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"也卷到大火里面"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"慕尼黑"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是从瓦砾堆里爬出来的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"眼睛里流着眼泪"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"嘴里念念有词"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"她能埋怨谁呢"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"花了整整三十五年"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"才医治了战争的创伤"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"但她已失去了青春"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"如今"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"巴伐利亚的啤酒"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"依然招引了四面八方的客"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"第二代的慕尼黑"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"比母亲更美丽、也更殷勤"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"但愿她不再和魔鬼交朋友"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把门户看得紧"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"接受母亲的教训"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"生活得更聪明……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"五月三十日在慕尼黑"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"市政府的宴会之后"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":6,"page_end":6}